name: White Yorkshire
description: Welcome to White Yorkshire (WSH)! We're a team of meme enthusiasts and blockchain experts on a mission to bring humor and community to cryptocurrency. Join us as we combine memes and digital currency to create a fun and inclusive space for crypto investors, meme creators, and fans of the adorable White Yorkshire Terrier. White Yorkshire (WSH) is a meme-inspired cryptocurrency project centered around the iconic White Yorkshire Terrier meme. With 3 trillion WSH tokens in circulation, WSH fosters a vibrant community where meme enthusiasts and crypto investors can trade, create, and enjoy White Yorkshire memes. Join us to spread joy and laughter through the power of memes!
